July 28, 2017 3:55 AM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of Pegasus Partners V, L.P.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Pegasus Partners V, L.P. specializes in buyout, middle market, turnaround, mature, and later stage investments. It seeks to invest in various sectors including building materials, business services, commodities, consumer products, energy, financial services, logistics, media, and security. It also invests in companies that focus on scarcity of food, water, energy and security, globally. The fund primarily invests in North America with a focus on the U.S.A. The fund prefers to invest in companies with equity investment between $50 million and $200 million.


99 River RoadCos Cob, CT 06807United StatesFounded in 2011



Phone: 203-869-4400

Fax: 203-869-6940








