Randall Wilson




                          Randall Wilson                          Strategic Advisor






Randall Wilson has over 25 years of financial and operational related experience with responsibilities ranging from business development, finance, accounting, IT, and operations. Prior to joining Pegasus, Mr. Wilson was the Chief Financial Officer, President and Vice President of New Oil and Refinery Operations at Universal Lubricants, a former Pegasus portfolio company.   Prior to Universal Lubricants, Mr. Wilson worked at KOCH Industries as Controller of the fertilizer division.  Prior to KOCH Industries, Mr. Wilson worked at Farmland Misschem in the Republic of Trinidad and Tobago as its Director of Finance.   Mr. Wilson has significant experience in multiple industries including agriculture, renewable energy, recycling and food retailing.




